===Etymology 4===
{{ja-spellings|h=あれ|吾|我}}
The long form of {{m|ja|あ|tr=a|t=[[I]], [[me]]}}. From {{suffix|ja|あ|tr1=a|れ|tr2=re|pos2=nominalizing suffix}}

Fell into disuse in roughly the [[w:Heian period|Heian period]],<ref name="DJR">{{R:Daijirin}}</ref> when it was replaced by {{ja-r|われ}}.

